data.description: Welcome home to Remington Cove?s Newest Addition! This spacious 3 Bed, 3 Bath home showcases stained cabinetry, stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, 2 bedrooms up & main floor living w/walk-in closets. Plenty of storage in the extended 2-car garage plus additional community parking spaces for guests. Enjoy maintenance-free living & the benefits of low association dues, lawn maintenance, sanitation, snow removal and professional management. This quiet neighborhood is located near walking paths, parks & shopping. Easy access to Hwy 94.
